"2  center-cut bacon slices, chopped","3  garlic cloves, minced","2 cups unsalted chicken stock (such as Swanson)","1 cup 1% low-fat milk","1  (10-ounce) package frozen butternut squash puree, thawed","10 ounce uncooked large elbow macaroni","3 cups chopped broccoli florets","1/2 teaspoon salt","1/2 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","5 ounces sharp cheddar cheese, shredded and divided (about 1 1/4 cups)"